name: Indie Robot Chair
description: Not many have a chair like this. In fact, only one person ever will. This vintage wooden chair boasts a classic design with a modern feel, reupholstered in a great indie fabric, robots covering it from left to right. This chair is like no other, perfect to add personality and individuality to any room. Whether used for reading, working, or just plain aesthetics, this chair cannot be outdone.

name: Geometric Triangle Tee
description: Perfectly imperfect, this hand screened tee could do with some loving. Hand printed onto an American Apparel tee, this shirt is an extremely limited edition of two in this blue on blue colourway. Only available in Large, this is a great oversized tee that looks amazing with shorts or skinny jeans, on guys and girls alike.
